<p><strong>Robert</strong><em> – 16 years old</em></p>
<p>Nothing is more fulfilling than sharing your passion with someone you love! Robert loves art and wants a family who’d share his interest. He loves to sketch and wants to try working with special effects make-up. When he grows up, he would like to work in a creative field, either as a special effects artist or an architect. When meeting people, Robert takes a little time to open up, but when he does, he has great stories to share. His ideal family would share his interest in the arts and would offer plenty of love, structure and support to earn his trust. With a family who will advocate for his educational needs andencourage him to engage with peers, Robert’s certain to reach his full potential.</p>
<p>To find out more information on Robert, click <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3wWm_pBftFQ">here </a>to watch an interview with him.</p>
